gov.ca.dmv.ease.bus.request.factory
Interface IBusRequestFactory

All Known Implementing Classes:
BusRequestFactory
public interface IBusRequestFactory

Description: Interface for an object producing service requests. This factory is to be called by DCS clients. The requests produces by the factory follow the Command Pattern and they can be executed directly. More creation methods will be added over time File: IExternalServiceRequestFactory.java Module: gov.ca.dmv.ease.ecs Created: Mar 17, 2009
